{"tid":2162012,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"殺入歐霸決賽  盧卡古安慰曼聯","createTime":"2020-08-18T01:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T08:04:50.000Z","uid":272077,"like":49,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"6ea67babf5abb866df7e50dff2e50c690cd7fa04","tid":2162012,"uid":272077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T01:46:42.000Z","msg":"國際米蘭前鋒盧卡古周一助球隊殺入歐霸盃決賽後，大讚於4強出局的前東家曼聯。<br />\n<br />\n國際米蘭周一在歐霸盃4強以5:0淘汰烏克蘭名牌薩克達，比利時中鋒盧卡古（Romelu Lukaku）在比賽中梅開二度，他賽後不忘安慰前東家、已4強止步的曼聯，「我覺得曼聯盡力了，他們有一個很好的球季，蘇斯克查執教得很好，球員也很出色。」盧卡古說。<br />\n<br />\n這位曼聯棄將點名看好美臣格連活，「美臣格連活、馬斯亞、華舒福正在冒起，我真替他們開心，我肯定曼聯下季會更出色。」看來，這位中鋒對曼聯仍然很有感情。<br />\n<br />\n談到國際米蘭的表現，他說：「大家都付出100%，無論在戰術和體能上都全力以赴，贏下這一場硬仗。」國際米蘭將於周五與西維爾在科隆爭奪今屆冠軍寶座。"},{"pid":"595bcd6ae0b7ffecf21956deb153e982d8575ee8","tid":2162012,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T01:48:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1708d112bcdc3d7f7afd15ec66428666572fd911","tid":2162012,"uid":45880,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T01:49:02.000Z","msg":"寸緊曼聯得4強實力？"},{"pid":"0985a64d75720fc02331c26fe6557750a5bbfc86","tid":2162012,"uid":272077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"595bcd6ae0b7ffecf21956deb153e982d8575ee8","tid":2162012,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T01:48:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T01:50:45.000Z","msg":"卡古不忘初心"},{"pid":"ac66137e6a660fe91efb4457bd1583d9f3ab2c6d","tid":2162012,"uid":99700,"like":28,"dislike":24,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T01:51:52.000Z","msg":"等佢地空難死哂先安慰啦"},{"pid":"dfe0ad051911ea0051fc0bb35483c40756886bf4","tid":2162012,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T01:54:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gi